      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute showroom condition\u2014honestly, it looks and smells like it just rolled off the lot! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, keeping it tucked away in the garage and meticulously detailed. It drives like a total dream and is looking for a new home where it'll be just as loved. You won't find a cleaner ride out there, so come take it for a spin before it\u2019s gone!",
