    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) in collector-tier condition. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure double VANOS system that delivers linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a torque-sensing M-Variable differential. To ensure structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been addressed as part of a rigorous preventative maintenance schedule. The chassis retains its factory-spec handling characteristics with fresh bushings and Sachs dampers. The paint depth is consistent across all panels, and the interior leather shows zero compression or bolster wear, reflecting a life of climate-controlled preservation. Truly a turn-key specimen for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
