    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that looks and drives as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. This car has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled garage, preserving its stunning deep-gloss finish, which remains free of swirls, rock chips, or door dings. Inside, the premium leather interior retains its original factory scent and supple texture, with absolutely no visible wear on the bolsters, carpets, or touchpoints. Every electronic feature and safety system functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach; the engine is whisper-quiet, and the transmission shifts with surgical precision. This vehicle comes complete with a documented service history from the original dealership, two sets of keys, and the original owner\u2019s portfolio. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a collector-grade example that will satisfy the most discerning enthusiast.",
      "price": 48500.0,
